# Prince (drag queen)

Prince (also known as Prince Marell) is the stage name of Prince de Castro, a Filipino drag performer who competed on the first season of Drag Race Philippines. She was the first contestant to be eliminated from the competition.
Filmography
* Drag Race Philippines (season 1)
* Drag Race Philippines: Untucked!
* Bring Back My Girls (2023)
